{"tid":1281502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：沒聽說新疆邊檢人員於中亞旅客手機裝監控程式","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T10:41:15.000Z","uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d713fe6463bb52a3e13136b4ee6941cb5032ef","tid":1281502,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人耿爽承認，在7月2日聯合國安理會一個閉門內部會議上，美國和德國偏離會議主題，對新疆政策進行無端指責，中方對此堅決反對，中國常駐聯合國代表已當場對兩國的錯誤言論，嚴厲批駁。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽表示，新疆事務屬中國內政，與安理會議程毫無關係，也不容任何外部勢力干涉，安理會是維護國際和平的莊嚴機構，奉勸有關國家拼棄雙重標準，遵守國際會議的要求，停止破壞安理會的團結，停止干涉別國的內政。<br />\n<br />\n另外，多間外國傳媒報道，新疆邊檢人員要求從中亞國家入境的旅客，交出手機，並在手機上秘密安裝應用程式，監控手機內的資料。耿爽表示，沒有聽說有關情況。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466446-20190703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466446-20190703.htm&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=0ba0f549\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466446-20190703.htm&h=703f7d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466446-20190703.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49be4fc9c6fcdba8630d73d214cb540cab98c397","tid":1281502,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"沒有沒有沒有~"},{"pid":"23afca46caaa5e0b2cb10a3e1846d5c32b92b065","tid":1281502,"uid":266805,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"你認有我先覺奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab10d368cd9b05e04cfcc67dd3278550017aface","tid":1281502,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"耿爽表示，沒有聽說有關情況"},{"pid":"94b8b6879c5eb36755cd7509d7a1a8e460deff01","tid":1281502,"uid":248131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"喺自己國家搞到人地就叫內政，咁大陸人喺第度比人搞就唔關你事，華為單野就唔好嘈生晒<br />\n成班生蕃，連外交官都講野唔經大腦"}]}